sov, N., Kapadia, A.: DECENT: a decentralized architecture for enforcing privacy in online social networks. PERCOM Workshops <strong class=\"EmphasisTypeBold \">2012</strong>, 326\u2013332 (2012)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=DECENT%3A%20a%20decentralized%20architecture%20for%20enforcing%20privacy%20in%20online%20social%20networks&amp;author=S.%20Jahid&amp;author=S.%20Nilizadeh&amp;author=P.%20Mittal&amp;author=N.%20Borisov&amp;author=A.%20Kapadia&amp;journal=PERCOM%20Workshops&amp;volume=2012&amp;pages=326-332&amp;publication_year=2012\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">9.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR9\">Libert, B., Paterson, K.G., Quaglia, E.A.: Anonymous broadcast encryption: adaptive security and efficient constructions in the standard model. In: Fischlin, M., Buchmann, J., Manulis, M. (eds.) PKC 2012. LNCS, vol. 7293, pp. 206\u2013224. Springer, Heidelberg (2012)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceDOI\"><a class=\"gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"CrossRef\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-30057-8_13\"><span><span>CrossRef</span></span></a></span><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Anonymous%20broadcast%20encryption%3A%20adaptive%20security%20and%20efficient%20constructions%20in%20the%20standard%20model&amp;author=B.%20Libert&amp;author=KG.%20Paterson&amp;author=EA.%20Quaglia&amp;pages=206-224&amp;publication_year=2012\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"C