 model. In: Fischlin, M., Buchmann, J., Manulis, M. (eds.) PKC 2012. LNCS, vol. 7293, pp. 206\u2013224. Springer, Heidelberg (2012)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceDOI\"><a class=\"gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"CrossRef\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-30057-8_13\"><span><span>CrossRef</span></span></a></span><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Anonymous%20broadcast%20encryption%3A%20adaptive%20security%20and%20efficient%20constructions%20in%20the%20standard%20model&amp;author=B.%20Libert&amp;author=KG.%20Paterson&amp;author=EA.%20Quaglia&amp;pages=206-224&amp;publication_year=2012\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">10.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR10\">Nilizadeh, S., Jahid, S., Mittal, P., Borisov, N., Kapadia, A.: Cachet: a decentralized architecture for privacy preserving social networking with caching. In: Proceedings of the 8th International Conference on Emerging Networking Experiments and Technologies, pp. 337\u2013348 (2012)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Nilizadeh%2C%20S.%2C%20Jahid%2C%20S.%2C%20Mittal%2C%20P.%2C%20Borisov%2C%20N.%2C%20Kapadia%2C%20A.%3A%20Cachet%3A%20a%20decentralized%20architecture%20for%20privacy%20preserving%20social%20networking%20with%20caching.%20In%3A%20Proceedings%20of%20the%208th%20International%20Conference%20on%20Emerging%20Networking%20Experiments%20and%20Technologies%2C%20pp.%20337%E2%80%93348%20%282012%29\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div>